v1.3

    - New maintainer: Sylvain Beucler
    - Android port
    - Can skip intro logo animation
    - Patches from Debian:
      - make music files optional
      - savegames optionally in $HOME (-DSAVES_IN_HOME)
      - data files location configurable (-DDATADIR)
      - bugfixes

v1.2

    - Fixed a bug that only seemed to be affecting some Linux environments.
    - GPLed the source.

v1.1

    - Holding space while viewing the auto map now allows you to scroll around much faster.
    - Some issues associated with boss dialog not appearing have been fixed.

v1.0

    - First public release of Meritous. 
